    <Filepath>OnBoardingKit/System/Library/OnBoardingBundles/com.apple.onboarding.mapsrap.bundle/Contents/Resources/en.lproj/MapsRAP.strings</Filepath>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>SPLASH_SUMMARY</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Apple Maps is designed to protect your information and enable you to choose what you share.</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">Apple「地圖」的設計可保護您的資訊並讓您選擇分享的內容。</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>SECOND_BULLET</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">You may submit additional information with your report to help solve the issue more effectively</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">您可以在回報問題時附上更多資訊，以協助我們更有效地解決問題</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>BUTTON_CAPTION</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Your report and associated data will be used to resolve the reported issue and improve Maps.</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">您的回報和相關資料將用於解決所回報的問題，以及改進「地圖」。</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>SPLASH_TITLE</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Maps Report an Issue &amp; Privacy</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">地圖回報問題與隱私權</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>BUTTON_TITLE_APPLETV</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">See how your data is managed</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">查看您資料的管理方式</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>FOOTER_TEXT</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">When you report an issue, Maps is designed to collect the minimum necessary personal information to assess your report and improve Maps.

Apple collects the following information:
• your Apple ID, to be able to notify you of a fix to your reported problem
• the device model, operating system version, region and language, timezone, navigation settings, and whether you are connected to Apple Watch or CarPlay, to better understand Maps’s capability and state at the time of your report
• a screenshot of the Maps app prior to filing the issue, the latitude and longitude, the zoom level, and the last search term you used, to better understand the context at the time of the reported issue
• the information you provide in the report, such as suggested new addresses, URLs, opening hours along with comments, and any uploaded photos

In some cases, Apple may also collect:
• your email address, if you grant the permission to communicate with you to clarify the issue or notify you of a fix
• the start and endpoints of your direction request, for directions issues
• your home or work addresses, for home or work location corrections
• the results from your last search, including the search terms that were used to provide those results, for search related issues
• the camera positions for imagery issues

When your issue relates to a third-party, Apple may provide the third-party with information from your reported issue to help fix the issue you identified. Apple only shares information with such third-parties when necessary to fix an issue and first seeks to delete any information from which you can be identified.

Apple may store the information you report in a manner that is associated with you for up to two years to better understand reporting trends. At all times, information collected by Apple will be treated in accordance with Apple’s Privacy Policy, which can be found at www.apple.com/privacy</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">當您回報問題時，「地圖」是設計為收集最少量的必要個人資訊以取用您的報告並改進「地圖」功能。

Apple會收集下列資訊：
• 您的Apple ID。用來通知您已修正回報的問題
• 裝置機型、作業系統版本、地區和語言、時區、導航設定以及是否連接Apple Watch或CarPlay。這些資訊可進一步地瞭解在您回報問題時，「地圖」的效能與狀態
• 在填寫問題報告前的「地圖」App螢幕快照、經緯度、縮放比率以及您最後一次使用的搜尋字詞。這些資訊可進一步地瞭解在您回報問題時，「地圖」所呈現的內容
• 您在報告中提供的資訊。例如建議的新地址、URL、營業時間和評價以及任何上傳的照片

在某些情況下，Apple可能也會收集下列資訊：
• 您的電子郵件地址。若您同意我們與您通訊以說明問題原因，或通知您已修正問題，則會收集您的電子郵件地址
• 您要求路線的起點和終點。用以修正路線問題
• 您的住家或公司地址。用以修正住家或公司位置
• 您上一次的搜尋結果，包含用來提供結果的搜尋字詞。用以解決與搜尋相關的問題
• 用來處理圖像問題的相機位置

若您的問題與第三方有關，Apple可能會提供您回報的問題資訊給第三方，以協助修正您指出的問題。Apple只有在必要時才會與此類第三方分享資訊以修正問題，並且會首先找出並刪除任何能識別您個人身分的資訊。

Apple可能會以與您相關的方式來儲存您回報的資訊，最長達兩年的時間，這是為了能更有效地瞭解報告的趨勢。在任何時間，Apple都會依照「Apple隱私權政策」的規定來處理收集到的資訊，請參訪：www.apple.com/tw/privacy</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>SPLASH_SHORT_TITLE</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Maps Report an Issue</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">地圖回報問題</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>THIRD_BULLET</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Apple may store the information associated with you for up to two years to better understand reporting trends</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">Apple可能會儲存與您相關的資訊，最長達兩年的時間，從而更深入瞭解回報趨勢</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>BUTTON_TITLE</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">See how your data is managed…</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">查看您資料的管理方式⋯</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>FIRST_BULLET</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Maps Report an Issue collects information to help solve reported issues. This information is stored in association with your Apple ID</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">「地圖回報問題」會收集資訊以協助解決回報的問題。此資訊會以與您的Apple ID產生關連的方式儲存</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
    </TextItem>
