    </TextItem>
    <TextItem>
      <Description/>
      <Position>BUTTON_CAPTION</Position>
      <TranslationSet>
        <base loc="en">Apple collects books usage data, not associated with your Apple ID, to improve Apple Books. Your searches, browsing, purchases and device trust score may be used to personalize your experience, improve the store, and prevent fraud.</base>
        <tran loc="zh-TW">Apple會收集書籍使用狀況資料（不會與您的Apple ID產生關聯）來改進Apple Books。您的搜尋、瀏覽、購買內容和裝置的信任分數可用來提供個人化的使用體驗，改進商店和防止詐騙。</tran>
      </TranslationSet>
